{"bangumi":{"date":"1979-10-27","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/be/43/187189_7lVzU.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/be/43/187189_7lVzU.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/be/43/187189_7lVzU.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/be/43/187189_7lVzU.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/be/43/187189_7lVzU.jpg"},"summary":"　『星のオルフェウス』は、1979年公開のサンリオのアニメーション映画である。英題は『Winds of Change』\r\n　『小さなジャンボ』、『親子ねずみの不思議な旅』、『チリンの鈴』などで、アニメーション製作を手がけたサンリオ映画製作部が、アメリカ人のスタッフと合同で製作した劇場用アニメーション。実製作期間6年、原画数15万枚、制作費26億円、70mmフィルムで製作･公開された大作。併映は、『MAGIC CAPSULE Godiego』\r\n　ギリシア神話の物語を5篇のオムニバスで綴った、アニメーション映画。\r\n　太陽神アポロンの息子、パエトーンは、父の持つ炎の馬車を無断で持ち出し、乗り回すが、馬車は次第に暴走を始め、ついに大空の果てに燃え尽きてしまう。","name":"星のオルフェウス","name_cn":"俄耳甫斯之星","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1979","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"赛璐珞","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1979年十月番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"70s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1979年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1979年10月","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"俄耳甫斯之星"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"变形记"},{"v":"Hoshi no Orpheus"},{"v":"Winds of Change"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1979年10月27日"},{"key":"片长","value":"80分钟"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":2,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":1,"7":0,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5},"total_episodes":1,"collection":{"on_hold":3,"dropped":7,"wish":8,"collect":5,"doing":1},"id":187189,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版","日本","美国","欧美"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},"bangumiData":{"title":"星のオルフェウス","titleTranslate":{},"type":"movie","lang":"ja","officialSite":"","begin":"1979-10-26T16:00:00.000Z","broadcast":"","end":"1979-10-26T17:27:00.000Z","comment":"","sites":[{"site":"bangumi","id":"187189"},{"site":"danime","id":"25557","begin":"2023-05-01T01:00:00.000Z","broadcast":"R/2023-05